freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I have knee pain most of the time - not sure if still connected to vaccine

Right Knee pain 13 days after my second dose of Pfizer & still very painful that I need to see my doctor & just gone from my acupuncturist.  I did have knee pain also 10 days after my first dose but lasted only for 2 days & just miraculously disaappe

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I had nausea, headache , sleepiness , 6 hrs after vaccination.  On the second day when I woke up, it was so itchy and sore by the site
